{"type": "article", "id": 22382, "title": "蓬松甜点座椅", "description": "", "date": "2016-02-17T07:30:11Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 16, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606155524AjpzBl5y3RQD2NZJ.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这组家具名为“soufflé”（舒芙蕾），灵感源于甜点舒芙蕾在烘烤中的膨胀状态。它的顶部是蓬松的奶油状，有松软的褶皱，而底部是坚固的织物面料。另有一块边桌使用了浅色的橡木圆桌面，都显得小巧可爱。丹麦设计师 Cecilie Manz 想要营造一种从一个岩石跳到另一个岩石的感觉，让这组家具有活泼有趣的特征。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606061555221DAn7F4KkNYTc2Jp.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.70293399\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606155522KlVLbuNjEckZaInJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.51711491\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606155523GT38pxEbc4nZzQmP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56845966\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606155523Ne8mo7RwtVXhz6Ei.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.57701711\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606155524hnoAyB28Dv51bkeq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.3007335\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p><br></p>\n\n\n"}